TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Evacuate! Intelligence indicates your base will be attacked by a strong enemy force in 6 minutes time. Scout quickly and transport yourself to one of the central hills, where you should be safe for a few minutes. You'll need some fighters to protect yourself as you land. Establish a base up on the hill and destroy the enemy geothermal power plant in the east.
